Imports System Imports System.IO Imports System.Net Imports System.Text
Public Class Snippet
Public Shared Function func(ByVal myURL As System.String, ByVal myQuery As System.String) As System.String
dim encoding as New UTF8Encoding()
dim datalength as Integer = encoding.GetByteCount(myQuery) dim utf8Bytes as Byte() = new byte(datalength -1) {} System.Text.Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(myQuery,0,myQuery.Length,utf8Bytes,0)
dim request as HttpWebRequest = DirectCast(WebRequest.Create(myURL), HttpWebRequest) request.Method = "POST" request.ContentType = "text/xml;charset=UTF-8" request.ContentLength = dataLength request.Timeout = 300000
dim str as Stream = Nothing try str = request.GetRequestStream() str.Write(utf8Bytes,0,utf8Bytes.Length) str.Close() dim resp as WebResponse = request.GetResponse() str = resp.GetResponseStream() catch wEx as WebException if wEx.Status = WebExceptionStatus.Timeout then return ("Request timed out") else return ("Error "+wEx.Message) end if end try
dim sr as New StreamReader(str, System.Text.Encoding.Default ) dim antwort as String try antwort = sr.ReadToEnd() catch ex as Exception return ("Error " + ex.Message) end try return antwort
End Function
End Class
